Text:
Hey Griboyan! Thanks for the upload. This is the most comprehensive Nusrat's collection in the pirate's world. Id tags are good too. Thought the bit rate is 128 for majority but its not a big deal in quwallis as they are more appreciated for lyrics and tempo than their instruments. You must come to Delhi once to enjoy their performance live. 

In case you find Live in New York, please upload it too. Thanks again.
